reviewText: I remember watching Walker, Texas Ranger as a kid, but as I grew older, the series remained largely forgotten until I had the pleasure of borrowing each season from a friend of mine. I enjoyed the series so much with each season, but grew frustrated and dismayed when my friend didn't have every season, and that included Season Seven, so I decided to buy it for myself, whatever the price was.The disc arrived in the mail in great shape, and within the time space of only a couple of days. I am so excited to have this movie, and Chuck Norris makes the best Texas Ranger ever! Too bad there weren't any more seasons made, as they would've all been great hits on their release dates. Soon, I will be able to own every season and it will be bought on amazon, due to their speedy service and the condition of their movies. This movie kicks some major butt!
